CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 14, 1956, pg. A18 reads: " New Arrivals - Mrs. Anna Mae Ashley smiles happily with her new twins, Michael and Michele, born the same night her aunt and uncle, Daniel and Anna Mae Jackson, who sing with the El Venos, were notified that the group won first prize on the Wilkens Amateur Hour. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Anna Mae Ashley holding twins Michael Ashley and Michele Ashley, in front of light colored curtain in hospital
